---

---
    <!-- Timeline -->
    <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline Line -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-blue-500 -ml-px"></div>
        
        <!-- Timeline Items -->
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <!-- Item 1 -->
          <div class="relative flex md:items-center">
            <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2"></div>
            <div class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 border-background mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
              <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">The Beginning</h3>
                <p class="text-foreground/80">
                  A group of systems thinkers met at COP29, united by a shared vision to address the global water crisis through innovation and collaboration.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <!-- Item 2 -->
          <div class="relative flex md:items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 pr-12 text-right">
              <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Our Mission</h3>
                <p class="text-foreground/80">
                  We committed to advancing SDG 6 and improving the lives of 1 billion people through resilient, equitable access to clean water.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border-4 border-background mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2"></div>
          </div>
  
          <!-- Item 3 -->
          <div class="relative flex md:items-center">
            <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2"></div>
            <div class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-500 border-4 border-background mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
              <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Global Expansion</h3>
                <p class="text-foreground/80">
                  Established teams in Dubai, Delhi, Vaduz, and Munich to create a truly global impact network for water innovation.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <!-- Item 4 -->
          <div class="relative flex md:items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 pr-12 text-right">
              <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Integrated Approach</h3>
                <p class="text-foreground/80">
                  Launched our three-pillar strategy: Venture Building, VC Fund, and PE Fund to address water challenges at every stage.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500 border-4 border-background mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  